## Purpose

Install and test recipient-owned handoff activation without a human/Codex
post-handoff nudge. This is intentionally non-code to avoid machine load.

## Steps

1. Maya installs a caller-scoped self-watchdog scheduled action.
2. Theo sends a T5c handoff containing test_hash.
3. Codex waits and observes only; it must not message Maya after Theo's
   handoff.
4. Maya's self-watchdog should reply with the test_hash if it sees the handoff.

